## Epic 4 — Season Averages Tab

### US-009 · Look up season averages by name and season
**Priority:** P0

> As a sports journalist, I want to type a player's name, pick a season, and instantly see their averages, so that I can fact-check a claim quickly without navigating through a profile.

**Acceptance criteria:**
- [ ] Name input and season selector are shown together on the Season Stats tab.
- [ ] Pressing Search or Enter triggers the lookup.
- [ ] If one player matches, their stats load immediately.
- [ ] Stats are displayed in a labelled stat-card grid.
- [ ] The season label (e.g. "2024–25") is shown alongside the player's name.

---

### US-010 · Disambiguate between players with similar names
**Priority:** P0

> As a journalist, I want to choose between multiple players who share a name, so that I get the right person's stats and not a different player.

**Acceptance criteria:**
- [ ] If the search returns 2 or more players, a picker listing all matching names appears before stats are loaded.
- [ ] Clicking a name from the picker immediately fetches that player's stats for the selected season.
- [ ] The picker disappears once a selection is made.

